{
  "value": "DESIGN_DECISION",
  "label": "Design Decision",
  "description": "Architectural decision documents (DESIGN.md §5.2). Examples: archetypes paper, FTS fireside outcomes. Identity by title — re-filing under the same title creates a new version.",
